TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(1,9,1);
$b1 = 2*$a1;
$c1 = random(1,200,1);

BEGIN_TEXT

By completing the square, the expression \(x^2+$b1 x +$c1\) equals
\( (x+A)^2+B\)  $BR where \(A=\) \{ans_rule(20) \} and \(B= \) \{ans_rule(20) \}

END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp( $a1 ) );

ANS(num_cmp( $c1 - $a1*$a1 ));

